description: Deeper Sounds of Nairobi is a dose of House music.Featuring guest DJs, Artists and Producers from Africa. Deeper Sounds of Nairobi is a promotional radio show recorded and produced in various corners of the world. These two shows are committed to showcasing musical talent coming out of Africa in the House/Dance Genre.

items.author: Jack Rooster(DSON)
items.content:
Having always been fascinated by the serenity of the ocean coupled
with that warm,salty breeze every time you hit the beach,this set was
one I had a really great time compiling.

I see a large bonfire,dancers on the African sands getting into the
groove of things as the evening breeze gently creeps in.

The full moon overhead seems to be chasing away the sun as the
magnificent golden ball elegantly disappears into the horizon.

Energies are steadily intensifying now ,drum tempo is rising,the mood
changes from gentle to more rigorous,people are breaking a sweat.

The final dark and yellow shimmer of the sleeping sun signals the
beginning of a new phase.

The moon is in full view now marking the start of a great night ahead.

To Sunrise we march!

Whether you are on Diani beach or Playa D'en Bossa, this set would be the perfect companion to a Sunset anywhere.

Enjoy.
J.R.
